# Petropavlovka, Zaigrayevsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Petropavlovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Zaigrayevsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 65 as of 2010.
Geography
Petropavlovka is located 36&nbsp;km northeast of Zaigrayevo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Novaya Kurba is the nearest rural locality.
